  • Classes in com.procom.filefly used by com.procom.filefly 
    Class and Description
    ChooseFileDialogFragment
    Handles the user input of selecting a file and draws the user interface for this interaction.
    ChooseFileDialogFragment.ChooseFileDialogListener
    Interface that the target fragment must implement in order to receive the result code of the choose file dialog window selection by the user.
    DocumentListAdapter
    The android.widget.BaseAdapter used to back the ListView hosted by the DocumentListFragment using Documents as the data model.
    MainActivity.SectionsPagerAdapter
    A FragmentPagerAdapter that returns a fragment corresponding to one of the sections/tabs/pages.
    SendFragment.FileUriCallback
    Provides the necessary methods for the Callback used by the Android Beam API for NFC file transfer using an array of android.net.Uris corresponding to the files being transferred.
